parameters:
Mage Relm: Is this the cage of Isheker... What a strange
coincidence.
Thief Nora: What do you mean by that?

Mage Relm: Have you forgotten already? The three-legged hawk
is the emblem of the demon Isheker, isn't it?

Mage Relm: That's why we ended up here, in the cage of
Isheker with the same name...

Thief Nora: This place has a really eerie atmosphere. Are
you sure it's safe to set up an ambush here...?

Mage Relm: Honestly, I don't really want to do it either!
But it wouldn't hurt to keep the Archmage in a good mood,
right?
Mage Relm: I can't forgive targeting mages above all else.
Priestess Sophia: Oh, what is it?
Clea: Is Isheker something important to you, Sophia-san?
Clea: If you ever feel like talking, please let me know.

Mage Relm: Alright, let's go! We need to find a place where
everyone can hide!

Priestess Sophia: I wonder what kind of expression Clea-
chan and the others will make if I tell them the truth...
hehehe.

Priestess Sophia: If the time comes for me to speak, it will
be when I reveal my true purpose.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
